376&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800\' class=\'thickbox\' title=\'Google Analytics Dashboard for WP\'>Instalar</a>)</span></li></ul></div>','no'),(137,'json_api_plugin_version','1.2.2','yes');
